### Arabic

يُدْخِلُ مَن يَشَآءُ فِى رَحْمَتِهِۦ ۚ وَٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ أَعَدَّ لَهُمْ عَذَابًا أَلِيمًۢا

### English

He admits whoever He wills into His mercy. As for the wrongdoers, He has prepared for them a painful punishment